Package org.jsonschema2pojo.model

Class EnumDefinition

java.lang.Object
org.jsonschema2pojo.model.EnumDefinition
public class EnumDefinition extends Object
Holds an enum types effective definition.

The definition of the enum can be decided by: "enum" (JSON-Schema) "enum" and "javaEnums" (JSON-Schema + jsonschema2pojo extension) "enum" and "javaEnumNames" (JSON-Schema + jsonschema2pojo extension)
